OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1775127603
OL,3,CPatients recalled for bone scans due
OL,4,Cto diagnosis issues
OL,6,FA Jersey Hospital review has
OL,7,Fidentified potential concerns
OL,8,Fregarding the diagnosis and treatment
OL,9,Frecommendations for some patients who
OL,10,Funderwent bone densitometry scans.
OL,12,FIt follows an independent review that
OL,13,Fhighlighted concerns about scans
OL,14,Fconducted between January 2017 and
OL,15,FJanuary 2022.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
