OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1775127603
OL,3,CPatients recalled for bone scans due
OL,4,Cto diagnosis issues
OL,6,FSpecialist independent consultants
OL,7,Fhave reviewed more than 1,000 patient
OL,8,Fnotes and found that in 20 cases, the
OL,9,Ftreatment and care a patient had
OL,10,Ffollowing their scan "fell below the
OL,11,Flevel that would have been expected".
OL,13,FThe consultants advised that around
OL,14,F250 patients should undertake a re-
OL,15,Fscan to "monitor any changes to bone
OL,16,Fdensity".
OL,18,FHealth and Care Jersey expects to
OL,19,Freach out to islanders who require a
OL,20,Fre-scan from next month, with
OL,21,Fadditional clinics arranged.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1775127603
OL,3,CPatients recalled for bone scans due
OL,4,Cto diagnosis issues
OL,6,FThey hope to complete all recall scans
OL,7,Fby the end of May this year.
OL,9,FThose who had a bone densitometry scan
OL,10,Fsince January 2022 are not thought to
OL,11,Fbe affected, according to Health and
OL,12,FCare Jersey.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, those who haven't been
OL,15,Fcontacted and offered a recall
OL,16,Fappointment by the end of this month
OL,17,Fare being advised that the issue "does
OL,18,Fnot affect them".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1775127603
OL,3,CPatients recalled for bone scans due
OL,4,Cto diagnosis issues
OL,6,FIn a statement, Simon West, Medical
OL,7,FDirector for Health and Care Jersey,
OL,8,Fsaid: "I would like to sincerely
OL,9,Fapologise to any patients who have
OL,10,Fbeen affected and recalled for a scan,
OL,11,Fas I understand receiving such news
OL,12,Fcan be unsettling.
OL,14,F"As soon as it became apparent that
OL,15,Fthere were potential issues with the
OL,16,Faccuracy of reporting of the results
OL,17,Fof DEXA scans, Health and Care Jersey
OL,18,Ftook steps to commission an
OL,19,Findependent review.
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1775127603
OL,3,CPatients recalled for bone scans due
OL,4,Cto diagnosis issues
OL,6,F"Following the findings of the review,
OL,7,Fwe have worked as quickly as possible
OL,8,Fto contact affected patients and to
OL,9,Frecall them for another scan.
OL,11,F"I can assure Islanders that they can
OL,12,Fhave confidence in our current DEXA
OL,13,Fservice, and I hope that the swift
OL,14,Faction Health and Care Jersey has
OL,15,Fundertaken shows that, as a
OL,16,Fdepartment, we continue to address
OL,17,Fissues that have been identified from
OL,18,Fprevious years.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1775127603
OL,3,CPatients recalled for bone scans due
OL,4,Cto diagnosis issues
OL,6,F"We are open and transparent when
OL,7,Fthese issues emerge, (and) the quality
OL,8,Fand safety of our services is of the
OL,9,Futmost importance to us."
OL,11,FPotential issues with the reporting of
OL,12,Fbone densitometry scans were
OL,13,Fidentified in September 2025 as part
OL,14,Fof work carried out during the review
OL,15,Finto the deaths of rheumatology
OL,16,Fpatients in Jersey.
OL,26,@oD@VpmoD@Zpn
