OL,3,CPatients recalled for bone scans due
OL,4,Cto diagnosis issues
OL,6,FAny patient with concerns about their
OL,7,Fbone scans is advised to contact
OL,8,FHealth and Care Jersey's Patient
OL,9,FAdvice and Liaison Service on 01534
OL,10,F443515 or PALS@health.gov.je.
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
